Package: openaps-ecu-sunspec
Version: __OPENAPS_VERSION__
Architecture: armv7ahf-vfp-neon
Maintainer: OpenAPS <bdbruin@gmail.com>
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends: openaps-base, openaps-inv-driver
Description: OpenAPS ecu-sunspec — Modbus/TCP + RTU SunSpec frontend.
 Installs /home/applications/ecu-sunspec/ecu-sunspec and its /etc/rcS.d/S99
 BusyBox init script. Exposes the fleet as SunSpec models over Modbus :502,
 subscribing to inv-driver telemetry over UDS.
